{"tid":2447269,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地劇《贅婿》爆紅「上門女婿」入贅成熱話 介紹費漲10倍至$18,000","createTime":"2021-03-15T05:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T06:48:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5d013bfe0884c0cf7a82770724f1d6d764167e0e","tid":2447269,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"商戰古裝穿越劇《贅婿》最近在內地熱播，連帶令「上門女婿」成為熱門話題。位於浙江省杭州市蕭山區、專門介紹「上門女婿」的「金點子」婚姻介紹所負責人李繼延向《蘋果》表示，最近的確多了人查詢「上門女婿」，形容「電話都打爆了」，並透露「上門女婿」介紹費，從20年前的1,500元人民幣（下同，約1,800港元），上漲到現在的15,000元（約18,000港元）。約會公司「香港婚活」（HK Romance Dating）負責人則表示，在港未遇過有男方主動提出「入贅」，或女方要求「上門女婿」。她指，內地部份男子出身卑微，為向上流動才選擇「入贅」手段，香港相對下比較多機會，且香港女生不提入贅，反而多強調「門當戶對」，注重男方生活水平和習慣。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210315/FK6DW3UKWBFBTAHN6APKQ6TN2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210315%2FFK6DW3UKWBFBTAHN6APKQ6TN2M%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDryGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=f440adac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210315%2FFK6DW3UKWBFBTAHN6APKQ6TN2M%2F&h=a17cfdc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210315/FK6DW3UKWBFBTAHN6APKQ6TN2M/</a>"},{"pid":"cc729094b1f27ed4c194171b10246e30fb6cbd43","tid":2447269,"uid":321374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"支那新聞冇興趣"},{"pid":"ae132bad2e6ce1fbec1a266a03c6f9af968b0a90","tid":2447269,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"食軟飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fecb628bad3a9809fee286c4c359d1d023c370d9","tid":2447269,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:48:17.000Z","msg":"小說原著其實算好睇+有深度, 原著後期仲會提倡民主思想, 又殺皇帝, 但係支那人呢唔會知呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}